# This file intentionally left blank.
# The keystore directory is used for the release signing key.
# Generate a keystore with:
#   keytool -genkeypair -v -keystore app/keystore/release.jks -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000 -alias studyfocus
# Then base64 encode it for GitHub secrets:
#   base64 -w 0 app/keystore/release.jks
